net-tools
  arp, ifconfig, iptunnel, iwconfig, nameif, netstat, and route. These programs (except iwconfig) are included in the net-tools package that has been unmaintained for years.
  Package that has been unmaintained for years.

ifconfig
  Deprecated, use ip instead.

iwconfig
  Deprecated, use iw instead.

lspci -k
  List pci hardwares.

lsusb -v
  List usb drivers.

dmesg | grep firmware
  Show firmware messages.

dhclient wlan0
  Get an IP address by DHCP.

ifdown wlan0
  Shutdown interface wlan0.

ifup wlan0
  Start interface wla0.
